Introduction

Atlantis Kitsune is an Korean-Japanese trot duo under nCH Entertainment. The duo consists of Sohee and Miyu. Both members were contestants on the survival show Trot Girls Japan. They made their Korean debut on August 9, 2024 with “Oh My!".
